column5: Any one know whats going on with the lake simcoe fishing message board? what a time to shutt her down  one more week of fishing  ... does any one have any lake conditions for lake simcoe Fridays 16 degree weather with rain ?

Funny I was wondering and asked the same thing on this forum a few days ago, but it never got posted!!  Do I smell or something???  As far as the LS Message board goes - I have no idea, but the timing is terrible!
I am thinking it was a unplanned shut down but this is displayed on the main page The site being serviced at this time. you can still get to classified and everything else but the forum
Oh it works but is just being worked on. Supposed to be up today!!!!
I just got a call from the ice.... for me to come drop in from the air. No water on the ice and very few people out there. Whities are ON !

When arent they On Wayne......ya just have to be ontop of them is all....lol Just going sounds like more fun. Dont run into anyone. If its as good as they say where yer going, you can bet there will be hundreds of OTHERS gathering round....lmao INCOMMING!!!!
I've got the all clear from my wife (she's taking the baby to see some of her friends) I'll be on my roof Wayne. You've got a tail hook right? Now where's my sunscreen?
maybe tomorrow at which time it will be today
